Package: dmft
Title: Age-Spatial-Temporal Modeling of Dental Caries (DMFT/dmft)
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ahmad", "Sofi-Mahmudi",
           email = "ahmad.sofimahmudi@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2460-2394"))
Description: Implements Age-Spatial-Temporal (AST) models for estimating
    dental caries burden (DMFT/dmft indices) at subnational level.
    Uses a two-stage approach: (1) random intercept mixed-effects model
    via 'lme4' with optional fixed covariates, and (2) AST kernel-smoothing
    of residuals across space, time, and age dimensions. Uncertainty is
    quantified via bootstrap. Supports any country given study-level data
    and a regional shapefile. Provides a complete pipeline from data
    cleaning through model fitting, diagnostics, projections, and
    publication-ready visualizations.
